OL,3,CEx-Chinese intelligence officer used
OL,4,C'Laughing Policeman' to torment couple
OL,6,FA former Chinese intelligence officer
OL,7,Fand her solicitor daughter who staged
OL,8,Fan "all-out war" on their neighbours
OL,9,Ffollowing a dispute over a hedge have
OL,10,Fbeen jailed.
OL,12,FSusan Chen, 61, and her daughter Linda
OL,13,FLu, 35, were convicted of causing
OL,14,Fserious alarm or distress to their
OL,15,Fneighbours, James and Lynn Smith, in
OL,16,Fthe village of Bassingham, near
OL,17,FLincoln.
OL,19,FA court heard problems started when Mr
OL,20,FSmith attempted to cut the hedge
OL,21,Fdividing their properties in July 2023.
