OL,6,FChen and Lu used a mobile phone linked
OL,7,Fto a camera to alert them when the
OL,8,Ffamily were outside their house. They
OL,9,Fused binoculars to spy on the family.
OL,11,FMr Smith made around 200 audio and
OL,12,Fvideo recordings documenting the
OL,13,Fproblems, while Chen and Lu ignored
OL,14,Fcommunity protection notices designed
OL,15,Fto curb the harassment.
OL,17,FLincoln Crown Court heard Mr and Mrs
OL,18,FSmith, who have two young children,
OL,19,Fbecame increasingly anxious because of
OL,20,Fthe problems.
