OL,6,FJudge James House KC said it was one
OL,7,Fof the most serious cases of its kind
OL,8,Fto come before the court.
OL,10,F"James and Lynn Smith had both been
OL,11,Fteachers for many years," he said.
OL,13,F"They had chosen Bassingham because it
OL,14,Fwas and is a lovely village to live."
OL,16,FHe said they were subjected to a
OL,17,F"persistent, calculated and appalling"
OL,18,Fpattern of behaviour.
OL,20,F"The verbal abuse was vile," Judge
OL,21,FHouse said.
