OL,6,F"In short the defendants terrorised
OL,7,Fthe Smith family."
OL,9,FChen and Lu represented themselves
OL,10,Fduring a five-week trial, alleging
OL,11,Fthey were the victims.
OL,13,FBut a jury took just two hours to
OL,14,Fconvict the two women of stalking.
OL,16,FThe jury heard Lu had no previous
OL,17,Fconvictions but Chen was previously
OL,18,Fconvicted of assaulting an elderly
OL,19,Fcouple while living in the village of
OL,20,FBalderton, near Newark, Notts, during
OL,21,F2020.
