OL,3,CEx-Chinese intelligence officer used
OL,4,C'Laughing Policeman' to torment couple
OL,6,FChen told jurors she had previously
OL,7,Fspent 14 years serving in the Chinese
OL,8,FArmy, rising to the rank of Major.
OL,10,FChen and Lu were were each jailed for
OL,11,Ffive and half years.
OL,13,FPC Jordan Bathie-Drexler, of
OL,14,FLincolnshire Police, said: "In almost
OL,15,F10 years of policing, I have never
OL,16,Fseen such persistent, relentless and
OL,17,Funprovoked offending by a suspect.
OL,18,FLinda Lu utilised her position as a
OL,19,Fregistered solicitor in order to carry
OL,20,Fout an all-out war on the victims of
OL,21,Fthis case."
